name: Light Garden Satellite
description:
Laser art created in LaserLewDude's closet. Lasers / Glass / Mirrors
Not a render. 
Discord Airdrop 2021

Dielectric glass panes, glass bookends and a few glass balls. 
Lasers:
638nm (red) through star field diffraction grating
488nm (pretty blue) through 120 degree line generator and 50 lines/mm diffraction grating for "blinds" effect
520nm (green)
